using mqtt with esp:
few brokers available: e.g broker.hivemq.com port 1883 is simple to use

Config menu e.g 
SSID:hg566
WPA Key:********
WPA AP Mode Key:configesp
Unit nr:1
Protocol:	OpenHab MQTT
Locate Controller: Use Hostname	
Controller Hostname: broker.hivemq.com
Controller Port:1883
Controller User:	
Controller Password:	
Sensor Delay:	10
Sleep Mode:	

topic structure: /<espname>/<device name>/<value name>;  e.g refer espmenu: /kkesp01/swgpio 0/Switch  (under device; edit)

mqtt topic viewer: https://www.hivemq.com/mqtt-toolbox ; e.g mqttbox, chrome extension
